                    a v:Point ;            
                    v:fullText "the existence of the right to request from the controller access to and rectification or erasure of personal data or restriction of processing concerning the data subject or to object to processing as well as the right to data portability;"@en ;
                    v:breadcrumb        "chapter III, article 13, point 2b"@en ;
                    v:breadcrumbLabel   "chapter III (Rights of the data subject), article 13 (Information to be provided where personal data are collected from the data subject), point 2b"@en ;
