<https://omc.co/5511993891773/7492/Chapter_III/Article_13/Point_2e>
                    a v:Point ;            
                    v:fullText "whether the provision of personal data is a statutory or contractual requirement, or a requirement necessary to enter into a contract, as well as whether the data subject is obliged to provide the personal data and of the possible consequences of failure to provide such data;"@en ;
