<https://omc.co/5511993891773/7492/Chapter_III/Article_13/Point_3>
                a v:Point ;            
                v:fullText "Where the controller intends to further process the personal data for a purpose other than that for which the personal data were collected, the controller shall provide the data subject prior to that further processing with information on that other purpose and with any relevant further information as referred to in paragraph 2."@en ;
                v:breadcrumb        "chapter III, article 13, point 3"@en ;
                v:breadcrumbLabel   "chapter III (Rights of the data subject), article 13 (Information to be provided where personal data are collected from the data subject), point 3"@en ;
